Theme/Base V3 3.0.0

	* New styles for a few various changes in Core.
	* Classname fix for new font-awesome.
	* Style updates for the user activity rework, user agent outputing, and new inline selection of
	  pagination limits.
	* Use the ConfigHandler for retrieving options in the site schema and site social links.
	* Make disabled form elements lighter than the non-disabled form elements to render a noticeable
	  difference between them.
	* Switch to ConfigHandler instead of static defines to support multi-site configuration scenarios.
	* Licensed footer and pre code styling
	-- Charlie Powell <charlie@evalagency.com>  Wed, 20 Jul 2016 02:16:08 -0400

